{
  "A store sells T-shirts for $12 and hats for $8. If 15 items were sold for $148, how many T-shirts were sold?": "",
  "6": "",
  "8": "",
  "7": "",
  "9": "",
  "Let t = T-shirts, h = hats. t + h = 15 and 12t + 8h = 148. Substitute h = 15 - t: 12t + 8(15 - t) = 148 → 4t + 120 = 148 → 4t = 28 → t = 7.": "",
  "A boat goes 30 km downstream in 2 hours and 30 km upstream in 3 hours. What is the speed of the boat in still water?": "",
  "8 km/h": "",
  "10 km/h": "",
  "15 km/h": "",
  "12.5 km/h": "",
  "Downstream: b + c = 15, upstream: b - c = 10. Add: 2b = 25 → b = 12.5 km/h.": "",
  "Two numbers have a sum of 20 and a difference of 6. What is the larger number?": "",
  "14": "",
  "12": "",
  "13": "",
  "10": "",
  "x + y = 20 and x - y = 6. Add: 2x = 26 → x = 13. The larger number is 13 and the smaller is 7.": "",
  "An investor puts $10,000 in two accounts earning 3% and 7%. If total interest is $460, how much is at 7%?": "",
  "$6,000": "",
  "$4,000": "",
  "$5,000": "",
  "$3,000": "",
  "x + y = 10000 and 0.03x + 0.07y = 460. Substitute x = 10000 - y: 300 - 0.03y + 0.07y = 460 → 0.04y = 160 → y = $4,000.": "",
  "A coffee blend mixes $6/lb beans with $10/lb beans. To make 20 lbs costing $7/lb, how many pounds of $6/lb beans are needed?": "",
  "15": "",
  "x + y = 20 and 6x + 10y = 140. Substitute y = 20 - x: 6x + 200 - 10x = 140 → -4x = -60 → x = 15 lbs.": "",
  "A taxi charges $2.50 base plus $1.50/mile. A rideshare charges $5.00 base plus $1.00/mile. At how many miles do they cost the same?": "",
  "3 miles": "",
  "5 miles": "",
  "4 miles": "",
  "6 miles": "",
  "Set 2.50 + 1.50m = 5.00 + 1.00m: 0.50m = 2.50 → m = 5 miles. Both cost $10.": "",
  "A rectangle has perimeter 30 cm. Its length is 3 cm more than its width. What is the length?": "",
  "8 cm": "",
  "9 cm": "",
  "12 cm": "",
  "10 cm": "",
  "2L + 2W = 30 and L = W + 3. Substitute: 2(W + 3) + 2W = 30 → 4W + 6 = 30 → W = 6, L = 9 cm.": "",
  "A class has 30 students. There are 4 more girls than boys. How many boys are in the class?": "",
  "b + g = 30 and g = b + 4. Substitute: b + (b + 4) = 30 → 2b = 26 → b = 13.": "",
  "A coin jar has nickels and dimes worth $3.50 total. There are 50 coins. How many dimes are there?": "",
  "25": "",
  "20": "",
  "30": "",
  "n + d = 50 and 5n + 10d = 350. Substitute n = 50 - d: 250 - 5d + 10d = 350 → 5d = 100 → d = 20.": "",
  "The sum of two numbers is 45 and one is three times the other. What is the smaller number?": "",
  "11.25": "",
  "9,": "",
  "x + y = 45 and y = 3x. Substitute: x + 3x = 45 → 4x = 45 → x = 11.25.": "",
